                        h2 Dorado’s Residences: Elevated Villa Living on the Scenic Tourist Corridor
                        h3 A Premier Coastal Vantage Point
                        p Dorado’s Residences occupies a truly privileged position along the iconic Tourist Corridor, serving as a gateway between the historic cultural center of San José del Cabo and the vibrant coastal energy of Cabo San Lucas. This luxury enclave offers more than just a stay; it provides an immersive experience where the raw beauty of the Baja desert meets the endless horizon of the Sea of Cortez.
                        p Ideally situated for those who demand both seclusion and connectivity, our community places guests within moments of championship golf, pristine beaches, and the region’s finest culinary and social scenes. Located 40 minutes from Los Cabos International Airport (SJD) and mere minutes from downtown, Dorado’s Residences offers the perfect equilibrium between serene privacy and convenient access to the best of Los Cabos.

        section.features
            .container
                .row
                    .col-12
                        h3 Curated Villa Accommodations and Refined Resort Living
                        p Dorado’s Residences redefines the vacation experience by merging the autonomy of a luxury residence with the comprehensive service of an upscale resort. These villas are meticulously crafted for families, executive groups, and extended-stay travelers who prioritize space, architectural detail, and seamless indoor-outdoor living.

                        h3 Luxury Villa Features
                        p Every residence is designed to serve as a private sanctuary, featuring expansive layouts that invite relaxation:
                        ul
                            li Multi-bedroom configurations optimized for privacy, including spacious ensuite bathrooms
                            li Open-concept living and dining salons designed for sophisticated group entertaining
                            li Professional-grade gourmet kitchens with premium finishes
                            li Private terraces featuring panoramic ocean views and bespoke outdoor lounging
                            li Fluid floor plans that embrace the gentle Baja climate
                            li Integrated smart-home technology, high-speed connectivity, and premium entertainment systems

                        h3 Community Lifestyle and Lifestyle Amenities
                        p Beyond the comfort of the residences, our community offers a curated suite of facilities designed to enhance your coastal lifestyle:
                        ul
                            li Magnificent ocean-view infinity pools and sun-drenched lounge enclaves
                            li Exclusive beach access or premier privileges at nearby coastal beach clubs
                            li Meticulously landscaped gardens and serene pathways for evening walks or morning yoga
                            li Dedicated concierge services for personalized tour coordination and seamless logistics
                            li Golf coordination and access to the region’s most prestigious championship courses
                            li Event support for milestone celebrations, executive retreats, and intimate gatherings

                        h3 The Definitive Choice for Group and Extended Travel
                        p Dorado’s Residences is the premier selection for those who view travel as an art form. Its residential-vibe accommodations and proximity to the Tourist Corridor’s finest assets make it the top-rated choice for:
                        ul
                            li Multi-generational family reunions and milestone celebrations
                            li Groups of friends and golf enthusiasts seeking a private social base
                            li Discerning travelers planning extended seasonal escapes
                            li Guests who demand the autonomy of a luxury home paired with resort-level prestige

                        p For visitors who seek an elevated villa experience that harmonizes the majestic scenery of Baja with the comforts of a private, high-end residence, Dorado’s Residences offers an unforgettable and sophisticated stay in the heart of Los Cabos.

